## 🗣️ Multilingual Voice Support

The platform now supports all 23 official Indian languages with high-accuracy AI transcription.

### Language Selection
Users are now prompted to select their preferred language immediately upon entering the complaint filing flow.
![Language Selection Overlay](/Users/rohitkunjam/.gemini/antigravity/brain/f1fb3d0a-d846-4444-abbc-7c97a43b3887/language_selection.png)

### High Accuracy Voice Mode
A new "AI High Accuracy" mode has been added, which uses Gemini 1.5 Flash to transcribe regional languages with much higher precision than standard browser APIs.
![Localized UI and Voice Toggle](/Users/rohitkunjam/.gemini/antigravity/brain/f1fb3d0a-d846-4444-abbc-7c97a43b3887/hindi_ui_toggle.png)

### Final Voice Flow & Hallucination Fix Demonstration
The integrated flow was verified after resolving a port conflict (SimpleHTTP was blocking port 8000). The final test confirms:
1. **No Hallucinations**: Standard inputs like "Hello" now yield direct response strings rather than Spanish/English translation explanations.
2. **High-Accuracy Form Filling**: Verbal complaints correctly update the "Description" field in real-time.
![Final Form Population Demo](/Users/rohitkunjam/.gemini/antigravity/brain/f1fb3d0a-d846-4444-abbc-7c97a43b3887/final_complaint_form_1774934333968.png)

